This module has the definitions for the C wrapper functions used to interface with the C++ XLA compiler. These are just for internal use. The nimxla, graph and literal packages export the public API.

In order to compile and link first unpack the XLA shared library and includes from the Elixir Nx repo at https://github.com/elixir-nx/xla/releases under /usr/local

The C wrapper code here is copied from the https://github.com/LaurentMazare/xla-rs Rust bindings.
